put this driver into kernel/drivers/staging/iio/imu/garnet/

modify the Makefile of staging/iio/imu/Makefile by adding
obj-y += garnet/

modify the Kconfig of staging/iio/imu/Kconfig by adding
source "drivers/staging/iio/imu/garnet/Kconfig"

remember select Garnet in the Kernel Make Menuconfig file to make sure it is
built.

